title: Luria Concedes to Kiggans in Virginia House Race
description: Representative Elaine Luria of Virginia, a Democrat on the House committee investigating the riot of Jan. 6, 2021, lost to Jen. A Kiggans, a Republican state senator.
dc:creator: Luke Broadwater and Emily Cochrane
category: House Select Committee to Investigate the January 6th Attack

media:content.media:credit: Kristen Zeis for The New York Times
media:content.media:description: Jen A. Kiggans, a Republican House candidate, talking to voters at a rally in Smithfield, Va., last month. Both women in the race were Navy veterans.
